title: Print, "Sky Between the Clouds (Kumoma no Sora), No. 3", ca. 1910
markings: In graphite, lower left: Sky between the Clouds
inscribed: Inscribed in black ink, lower left: [Japanese characters] / no. 3 / Kumoma no Sora.
